Name: chardiff
Version: 1.0.1
Summary: Compare 2 strings and highlight differences
Home-page: https://github.com/yamatt/python3-chardiff
Author: Matt Copperwaite
Author-email: matt@copperwaite.net
License: UNKNOWN
Description: # CharDiff
        
        Take 2 strings as arguments and show the difference between them
        
        ## Installation
        
            pip3 install chardiff
        
        ## Usage
        
            python3 -m chardiff "string1" "string2" --color red
        
